data.description: Welcome to beautiful Bridgeport subdivision in Sneads Ferry.  Located just minutes from area beaches this 3 bedrooom 2.5 bath home has so much to offer.  Downstairs features a spacious open living area with fireplace, eat-in dining area, and chefs dream kitchen with center island. Upstairs you will find three bedrooms, 2 full baths and the upstairs laundry room.  The seller is even leaving the washer and dryer! The master suite features trey ceilings, walk-in closet, seperate tub and shower, and a dual vanity.  Spend your weekends and evenings at the community pool or playground area located within the neighborhood.  Don't let this one slip by.  Schedule your showing today!
